data.description:
Exciting opportunity to reside in one of Monmouth County's most coveted communities! 

This charming Dutch Colonial residence is nestled in the heart of WANAMASSA, offering an array of desirable features.

Upon entry, you're greeted by a spacious living room boasting a cozy WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE, complemented by an adjoining sunroom flooded with natural light. Entertain with ease in the formal dining room, while the updated kitchen boasts Stainless Steel appliances, silestone counters, and newer subway tiles. 

Upstairs, discover four well-proportioned bedrooms and an updated full bath, providing comfort and convenience for family and guests alike. Outside, the expansive fenced-in backyard beckons for leisure and relaxation, boasting a paver patio and firepit, ideal for entertaining.

Additional amenities include a full basement offering ample storage space and a dedicated laundry area. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity to elevate your lifestyle in a prime location. Act now to seize this remarkable offering!
